articles.title: Tadej Pogacar takes a break after fatigue of Tour de France - Cyclingnews
articles.description: UAE Team Emirates leader skips inaugural European Climber Championships
articles.content: Tadej Pogačar ended the Tour de France with a series of attacks on the Champs Elysees and a new power threshold but has opted to take a break from racing to recover from his testing three-week battle… [+2329 chars]
